{"tid":1235230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應警民衝突暴動定性　曾偉雄指違法行為須按法律分類","createTime":"2019-06-17T05:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T05:40:23.000Z","uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"13b7ebceea26a089285b97f6809f7ae42cba2ada","tid":1235230,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:40:23.000Z","msg":"金鐘上周三因為示威者反對修訂逃犯條例，與警方發生衝突，政府及警方事後將事件定性為暴動。<br />\n<br />\n警務處前處長曾偉雄被問到，有意見要求更改暴動的定性，他以手機短訊回覆本台，表示香港作為一個法治社會，違法行為必須按法律分類。若有人認為特區政府和警方就事件的定性法理上不恰當，可提出自己的法律觀點，以便社會作出客觀和公正的評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463369-20190617.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463369-20190617.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0uwQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=da27b43a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463369-20190617.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=95337b27\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463369-20190617.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n落左台就講人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}